data.description: Spacious home in Ozark..located south of Ozark South ele. Split foyer style (option to go upstairs or downstairs at the entry)..3 BR's, 1 full bath upstairs, 4th BR living area, laundry room, bath with step-in shower and garage downstairs. Access to the basement from the exterior is thru the garage..high speed internet is available, there is a HUGE backyard, enclosed with a chain link fence. Owner has had a large garden and chickens in the past. Roof, vinyl siding were replaced appr 9 yrs ago. AC and furnace were replaced appr 5 yrs ago. Financing of the home will be required to be conventional (or cash is fine). (Qualifications for FHA,VA and USDA will not be met).Solar panels have been installed and there are options for the cost and pay out  be assumed by the new owners . Viewings to be evenings and weekends plz.
